Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:59.44,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I scowled at the wind blowing\Nat my window of boredom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:07.47,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could turn away\Nthe awkwardness I was feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:15.65,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:21.17,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I nod noncommittally at today\Nas I hold it in my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:26.55,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,projecting myself a little exaggeratedly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:31.93,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that\Nsomething is about to change
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:37.26,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you\Ncalling out to my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:43.86,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Peeking up at cloudy skies,\NI sense what's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:51.89,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's reach out our hands\Nwith courage stronger than ever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:56.83,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and shadow are both still far off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:02:03.17,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but even so, we want to know\Nthe reason for this kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:10.64,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look now, beyond the brilliance\Nthat goes by nobody's name
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:18.67,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,before it all becomes a thing of the past
