Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.48,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a screening of the movie in the\NAV room. We are already there.... Chitanda
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.07,0:24:08.00,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight it turns to love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:11.75,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me in a pleasant dream
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.78,0:24:15.75,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that you find me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.78,0:24:21.12,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Our snooze-time date
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.34,0:24:41.34,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat of your budding warmth troubles me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.10,0:24:52.10,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand how I feel yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.49,0:24:58.96,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't supposed to be\Nany significance in your glance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.99,0:25:04.39,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's the same one\Nyou give all your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.42,0:25:10.10,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The tiny wishing star fading\Ninto the morning light
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.13,0:25:15.11,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and the magic it works during the night\N(I wish you would notice)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.14,0:25:18.07,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight it turns to love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.10,0:25:21.82,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me in a pleasant dream
